Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy got into a fight with Darky over training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he realized that he didn’t truly understand his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, Wolffy understood his father’s love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the two made amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you guys found any anachronists?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have forgotten to search somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s search again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we don’t? It’s not like we’ll find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that I couldn’t find my cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a dark—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a dark swan over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about a dark swan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and search for anachronists!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don’t we search that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has Wolffy been acting so strangely lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let them discover Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he’s doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Red dates, ginger slices, ginseng…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need one more ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it turnips or is it corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need a goat! Then the mutton soup will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. If my son is working so hard to catch goats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats are very cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who’s been following me lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by the way you’re sneaking that you’re no good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strong aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re no—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn’t thought that this cloaked guy would be so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son has already made friends with the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to work with me to capture them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve got a tall stature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice face,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and a kind smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly admire you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want you to be my captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be my apprentice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so good to be praised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to act colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I was just about to go hunt goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can’t let the goats see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t need to catch goats yourself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Young people today are quite respectable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m making sure you can’t leave, so the goats won’t find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s taking that guy so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not that impatient, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll have to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the goats are way too powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m no match for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we just stay home and relax for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with the mess in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It just got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re a wolf that’s afraid of conflict, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that I’d have to take matters into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to catch goats this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I said so,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t actually go catch goats, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But faking an injury isn’t going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If faking it doesn’t work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,jumping down from here might…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I should think of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You did get quite badly injured this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m no match for them, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m avenging you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats are very cunning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As captain, I shall bring you justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let you be endangered because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be sure to bring a goat back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With the state of your body now, there’s nothing you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it’s just a piece of goat wool,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will still bring it back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I want wool for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to make soup without a goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll suck it up and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve been searching all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll eat an apple and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my apple! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can rest at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Darky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing the goats aren’t nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Paddi doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this frog so dodgy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knocked out my frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be asking who threw my apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it even worse by switching them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don’t show yourself, I’m coming over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, then! I’m not scared of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d like to see who dares to mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s taking them so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’d they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't even paid back my apple yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,are you slacking off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I was searching for anachronists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, there was a weird person acting aggressively in the bushes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but they suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it have been an anachronist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go take a look, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t think all of the goats would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I was quick enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are goats, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you stopping me from catching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Captain. The goats of today are very powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t just rush in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t they just some goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,not
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see just how powerful those goats really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They do seem quite powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He was that strange person on the other side of the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf is with him, so he might be an anachronist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anachronist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s… It’s Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A… A wise man knows when to step down! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re catching up to us! What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t possibly outrun airplanes with just two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you fly the plane a little more stably?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve been caught! Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,—Take this—　—this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, operating mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Wolffy! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry. As long as we find Werewolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we’ll be able to find the anachronist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve escaped them at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who I am doesn’t matter. What matters is:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,do you now believe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that your son has truly befriended goats?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
